\n\n[caption id=\"attachment_99\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\" caption=\"Handcrafted mugs &amp; accessories\"]<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-99\" title=\"3238854525_9722a34363\" src=\"http://www.nethaat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/3238854525_9722a34363-300x199.jpg\" alt=\"Handcrafted mugs &amp; accessories\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" />[/caption]\n\n Hand made items are an expression of the designer\'s creativity. They are exclusive and make unique gifts. The hand sewn kurta or delicately crafted photo frame you present to your loved one will be a one-of-a-kind piece he/she will cherish forever. There is no doubting the fact that an attractive hand-made item will grab more eyeballs than the typical Valentine\'s Day gift from a known consumer brand. In fact, you may be surprised how many of your colleagues and friends may have gifted their companions the same gifts you bought from your city\'s popular mall. Make Valentine\'s Day more about appreciating your loved one with a gift fraught with value and meaning than just buying him/her the most advertised V-day product in showrooms.\n\n \n\n[caption id=\"attachment_100\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\" caption=\"Gift differently!\"]<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-100\" title=\"4285940034_5232ce6ccf\" src=\"http://www.nethaat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/4285940034_5232ce6ccf-300x168.jpg\" alt=\"Gift differently!\" width=\"300\" height=\"168\" />[/caption]\n\n<strong>For Her</strong>\n\n<strong> </strong><strong>Hand made jewellery: </strong>Jewellery is a great choice for women of all ages.  You can choose gold plated earrings, antique Kundan Meena jewellery or the more contemporary hand crafted earrings and necklaces that your loved one can wear to casual or formal occasions. You can opt for beaded, sequined and heavily embellished jewellery or minimalist designs, based on your wife/girlfriend\'s preferences.\n\n<strong> </strong><strong>Hand sewn kurtas: </strong>If your companion is a fashionista, add some sparkle to her wardrobe by gifting her a hand woven kurta. Most of these kurtas come in eco friendly dyes, so your loved can make an eco friendly statement as well.\n\n <strong>For Him</strong>\n\n<strong> </strong>It is always difficult shopping for a man. There just arent enough gift options to choose from. Wallets and watches have become passé. Unlike women, most men dont get excited over clothes and accessories. A common yet meaningful gift is a beautifully embellished photo frame with a picture of you and your companion. When the photo frame is hand-made, its value is all the more enhanced. Hand made paper diaries, though not exactly romantic, can also serve as a useful gift for your husband.\n\n Surprise your companion with a hand crafted gift and earn brownie points. Strengthen the bonds of love and pave the path for a deeper relationship by making the right choice of Valentine\'s Day gifts.","This Valentines Day express your love with Hand Crafted Gifts","","publish","open","open","","this-valentine%e2%80%99s-day-express-your-love-with-hand-crafted-gifts","","","2011-02-10 13:34:11","2011-02-10 13:34:11","","0","http://www.nethaat.com/blog/?p=94","0","post","","3");
