\n\nWoodwork is an ancient craft that has perhaps been known to mankind for the longest time ever. Ever since man learned to carve wood, he has been using this versatile material to create innumerable things including utensils, weapons, furniture, shelter and decorative items. Although the other uses have slowly been taken over by other stronger or more durable material, decorative items in wood are still just as popular as ever.\n\n<strong>The appeal of wooden crafts</strong>\n\nThe evolution of wood crafting techniques and tools has made it much easier to create stunning handicrafts using this base material today. However, there are many master craftsmen in India who still favour the use of traditional tools such as chisels, saws and hammers to create truly unique wooden decorative pieces.\n\nOne of the main reasons why wooden handicrafts continue to hold their strong position in the decorative items market is that they are resilient and easy to maintain. These items can be transported even across countries without a single scratch marring the finish. A simple brushing or cleaning with a cloth is all that is required to keep your wooden artefact in mint condition. Even the age old wooden items that hung in your grandfathers home can be restored to beauty with a quick coat of varnish.\n\n<strong>\n\n[caption id=\"attachment_139\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"300\" caption=\"Intricate Wooden design \"]<a href=\"http://www.nethaat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/4.2.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-139\" title=\"4.2\" src=\"http://www.nethaat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/4.2-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"Intricate Wooden design \" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a>[/caption]\n\n</strong>\n\n<strong>Wood lends to many options</strong>\n\nWood is one material that lends itself to any kind of decor. Although many people associate wood with ethnic interiors, there are many offices where wooden figurines or embossed wall pieces lend grace to the reception area. Wooden lattice work screens can be found at many elite hotels and restaurants as separators. Antiques made of wood are ageless decorative pieces that fit in just as perfectly into a cosy home as in a formal conference hall. A drab, colourless room can be transformed into an elegant area by using the right kind of wood decorative pieces.\n\nThere is a huge range of options to choose from when you want a wooden decorative piece to brighten up your home or office. An intricately carved wooden frame can be used to showcase a simple painting. A wood carved representation of an object or a well known figure can lend a personal touch to a room or shift focus of beholders to a specific theme. For example, a shipping business may have an elaborate carved ship in its reception area.\n\nWood has been the favoured material for hundreds of artisans because of its versatility and it will continue to grace the homes and offices of many across the world for ages to come. Be it a gift item or a decorative piece that you want in your home, a wooden artefact is the perfect addition to any room.","Woodwork- The Best Decorative Pieces for Your Home","","publish","open","open","","woodwork-the-best-decorative-pieces-for-your-home","","","2011-03-07 16:44:18","2011-03-07 16:44:18","","0","http://www.nethaat.com/blog/?p=138","0","post","","0");
